backend/api-docs.title: API Documentation with Swagger/OpenAPI
backend/api-docs.description: This guide covers how to document your Spring Boot REST APIs using Swagger/OpenAPI 3.0, making them more accessible and easier to understand for other developers.

backend/database.title: Database Integration
backend/database.description: This guide covers database integration with PostgreSQL, including database design, JPA/Hibernate configuration, and best practices for data modeling.

backend/jpa-hibernate.title: Data Access with JPA and Hibernate
backend/jpa-hibernate.description: This guide provides a deep dive into using JPA (Java Persistence API) and Hibernate with Spring Boot, covering advanced concepts and best practices.

backend/overview.title: Backend Development with Spring Boot
backend/overview.description: This guide provides a comprehensive introduction to backend development using Spring Boot, Maven, and PostgreSQL. Whether you're new to backend development or looking to expand your knowledge, this guide will help you understand the fundamentals and best practices.

backend/project-setup.title: Project Setup and Structure
backend/project-setup.description: This guide will walk you through setting up a Spring Boot project with all necessary dependencies and configurations.

backend/rest-api.title: REST API Basics
backend/rest-api.description: This guide covers the fundamentals of building RESTful APIs with Spring Boot, including best practices, request/response handling, and common patterns.

backend/security.title: Security Implementation
backend/security.description: This guide covers implementing security in Spring Boot applications, including authentication, authorization, and best practices for securing your API.

frontend/backend-integration.title: Backend Integration
frontend/backend-integration.description: This guide covers how to integrate your Next.js frontend with a backend API, including setting up API clients, handling authentication, and managing API calls.

frontend/components.title: Component Development
frontend/components.description: This guide covers how to create and structure components in Next.js using TypeScript and TailwindCSS, including best practices and common patterns.

frontend/overview.title: Frontend Development Overview
frontend/overview.description: This guide provides an overview of modern frontend development using Next.js, TypeScript, React, and TailwindCSS. Each section links to detailed documentation for in-depth learning.

frontend/project-setup.title: Project Setup and Configuration
frontend/project-setup.description: This guide covers how to set up a new Next.js project and understand its basic configuration.

frontend/state-management.title: State Management
frontend/state-management.description: This guide covers different approaches to managing state in Next.js applications, from local component state to global state management solutions.

fundamentals/overview.title: Fullstack Development Fundamentals
fundamentals/overview.description: This guide provides a comprehensive overview of the fundamental concepts and technologies needed to build a fullstack web application. It covers both frontend and backend development basics, along with essential tools and practices.

index.title: Introduction to Web Development
index.description: Welcome to our comprehensive web development guide! This wiki serves as a learning resource and reference for modern web application development. Whether you're just starting or looking to expand your knowledge, you'll find detailed information about various aspects of web development.
